SUMMARY:IMPROV 100 SUNDAYS 3:30 pm- Intro to Improv: Say Yes!\, SPRING'26
DESCRIPTION:Discover Unexpected Productions’ philosophy of improvisation\, developed over our 43 years of improvising in Seattle! \nYou’ll learn how to actively listen\, to use your own life to create collaborative stories\, and you’ll work on the fundamental principles of improvisation: what it means to say\, “Yes\, And”\, how to tell stories that include everyone in the room\, how to stop worrying about failing\, and the games and concepts behind what we do on stages around the world! \nUnder the guidance of one of our best Seattle improv teachers\, you will learn to:· \n\nBe a Better Listener\nConquer Fears\nSpark Creativity\nMeet New People & Make New Friends\nBecome a Better Problem Solver\nGain Confidence·\nFail With Grace (and Maybe Even Enjoy It)\nSay Yes More in Your Life\nGet Out of Your Comfort Zone\nBecome a Better Public Speaker\nDiscover More About Yourself\n…and have a blast doing it!\n\nTime and Dates: Sundays for eight (8) weeks\, from March 22 to May 27\, 3:30pm to 6:00pm (No class on April 5th) \nNOTE: Attendance at the first session of your course is mandatory as it sets the agenda for the entire quarter. If you think you will have to miss the first class\, please consider registering for the next quarter. \nNo Prerequisites. All students begin at this level\, even those with existing improv experience. It’s a prerequisite to the other levels. \nLocation: 5700 6th Ave St\, Suite 109\, Umbrella Room\, Seattle\, WA 98108 (In Georgetown\, south of downtown\, with plenty of parking.) \nMaximum Students: 16 \nCost: Ticket price $295.00 \nAge: 18 and above \n**Cancellation policy: If you must cancel before the first class\, we can only offer credit towards the same level class next quarter. We are unable to offer refunds. If you cancel after the first class we cannot offer credit towards a future class. Again\, we are unable to offer refunds.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-100-sundays-330-pm-intro-to-improv-say-yes-spring26/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE\, 1315 NW Mall Street\, Suite 4\, Issaquah\, WA\, 98108\, United States
CATEGORIES:Education
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/100-Sunday.jpg
GEO:47.5520122;-122.3251523
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE 1315 NW Mall Street Suite 4 Issaquah WA 98108 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=1315 NW Mall Street\, Suite 4:geo:-122.3251523,47.5520122
END:VEVENT
